### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/v1

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Root Endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/

###
### MOVIES
###

### Get all movies (default pagination)
GET {{apiUrl}}/movies

### Get movies with custom pagination
GET {{apiUrl}}/movies?page=1&limit=5

### Get specific movie by ID
# The Fellowship of the Ring ID
GET {{apiUrl}}/movies/5cd95395de30eff6ebccde5c

### Get another movie
# The Two Towers ID
GET {{apiUrl}}/movies/5cd95395de30eff6ebccde5d

###
### CHARACTERS
###

### Get all characters (default pagination)
GET {{apiUrl}}/characters

### Get characters with custom pagination
GET {{apiUrl}}/characters?page=2&limit=20

### Get specific character by ID
# Gandalf ID
GET {{apiUrl}}/characters/5cd99d4bde30eff6ebccfea0

###
### REVIEWS
###

### Create a review for The Fellowship of the Ring
POST {{apiUrl}}/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "movieId": "5cd95395de30eff6ebccde5c",
  "userName": "John Doe",
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "An absolute masterpiece! The Fellowship of the Ring set the standard for epic fantasy films."
}

### Create another review
POST {{apiUrl}}/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "movieId": "5cd95395de30eff6ebccde5d",
  "userName": "Jane Smith",
  "rating": 4,
  "comment": "The Two Towers is amazing, though not quite as captivating as the first one."
}

### Create a review without comment (optional field)
POST {{apiUrl}}/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "movieId": "5cd95395de30eff6ebccde5c",
  "userName": "Sam Wilson",
  "rating": 5
}

### Get all reviews
GET {{apiUrl}}/reviews

### Get reviews for a specific movie
GET {{apiUrl}}/reviews?movieId=5cd95395de30eff6ebccde5c

### Get reviews with pagination
GET {{apiUrl}}/reviews?page=1&limit=5

### Get specific review by ID (replace with actual ID from created review)
GET {{apiUrl}}/reviews/1

###
### ERROR SCENARIOS
###

### Invalid rating (should return validation error)
POST {{apiUrl}}/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "movieId": "5cd95395de30eff6ebccde5c",
  "userName": "Test User",
  "rating": 6,
  "comment": "This should fail - rating too high"
}

### Missing required fields (should return validation error)
POST {{apiUrl}}/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userName": "Test User",
  "rating": 5
}

### Invalid movie ID (should return API error)
GET {{apiUrl}}/movies/invalid-id-12345

### Invalid pagination parameters
GET {{apiUrl}}/movies?page=-1&limit=1000
